name: fantasy-3136/solana-trading-bot-on-telegram
description: A Solana trading bot integrated with Telegram that monitors token prices and on-chain liquidity, routes swaps through Solana DEX aggregators (e.g. Jupiter), and executes buy/sell orders via secure wallet keys. Includes risk controls, PnL tracking, and chat commands for strategy control.

name: fantasy-3136/discord-video-stream-bot-developement
description: A Discord media streaming bot built with discord.js, designed to play and control video/audio in voice channels using a standard bot account. Supports slash commands, queues, pause/resume, and responsive status embeds, with an event-driven, scalable architecture.
